GENERAL ASSEMBLY OF NORTH CAROLINA
SESSION 2025
H 1
HOUSE BILL 757
Short Title: Funds for Joyful Soul Treasures. (Public)
Sponsors: Representative K. Brown.
For a complete list of sponsors, refer to the North Carolina General Assembly web site.
Referred to: Appropriations, if favorable, Rules, Calendar, and Operations of the House
April 7, 2025
1 A BILL TO BE ENTITLED
2 AN ACT TO APPROPRIATE FUNDS TO JOYFUL SOUL TREASURES, INC.
3 The General Assembly of North Carolina enacts:
4 SECTION 1. There is appropriated from the General Fund to the Office of State
5 Budget and Management the sum of thirty-one thousand dollars ($31,000) in nonrecurring funds
6 for the 2025-2026 fiscal year to provide a directed grant to Joyful Soul Treasures, Inc., a nonprofit
7 organization, to assist the organization with its "Safe Haven for Safe Sex" project, which is a
8 campaign aimed at enhancing sexual health education and awareness among adolescents aged 13
9 through 18. The initiative focuses on empowering young people with essential knowledge and
10 skills, reducing stigma and misconceptions regarding sexual health.
11 SECTION 2. This act becomes effective July 1, 2025.
*H757-v-1*

